tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 10:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们自己看好量能就行了 我今天教过了", "lou": 1871, "content_length": 34, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775615675}, {"pid": 863838307, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 10:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "除了石油之外 没多少个绿的<br/>兆易创新是绿的 <br/>我昨晚说了我的看法。目前验证", "lou": 1872, "content_length": 66, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775616302}, {"pid": 863839769, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 47, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 10:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863839050,45974302,3488]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38222910]lovecan9[/uid] (2026-04-08 10:49):[/b]<br/><br/>信了狼大的。本来做好开盘绿清准备了，最后255红着走了，舒服。[/quote]<br/>那是你运气好  如果今天不是TACO  做好一个地板的准备", "lou": 1873, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 863839050, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775616866}, {"pid": 863839900, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 10:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863839695,45974302,3489]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-04-08 10:54):[/b]<br/><br/>又来了一波卖盘，看看能不能接住[/quote]<br/>我都和你说了  现在看什么  看量能 量能没有回退1000E以上今天就不是高点。", "lou": 1874, "content_length": 70, "reply_to": 863839695, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775616919}, {"pid": 863843840, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 57, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 11:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "所以为什么我早上早早来这里说今天要怎么操作。你们知不知道操作体系的重要性了", "lou": 1875, "content_length": 74, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775618427}, {"pid": 863844649, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302,